window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Book Two <i>SLEEPY HOLLOW: Bridge of Bones</i> is NOW AVAILABLE</p> <p>JASON CRANE just turned seventeen years old. </p> <p>He's a <i>STAR WARS</i> fan and a history geek. He doesn't believe in ghosts or the afterlife. He doesn't believe in psychic powers or tarot cards. He doesn't believe in the Headless Horseman. </p> <p>But Sleepy Hollow will change all that. Because Jason Crane has a heritage to claim. Jason Crane has a Gift to discover. And Jason Crane has an old enemy who will RISE HEADLESS AND RIDE.</p>"; 
